						               													<description>Consortium is a print &amp;amp; play dice game for 1 to 6 persons in which the players take the roles of powerful businessmen, trying to acquire the most worthy concessions  possible. The concessions concern three types of natural resources (energetic resources (E), metals (M) and water (W)).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal is to score the maximum possible number of points. The points of each player are summed at the end of the game and are attributed for the number of their concessions, for their political influence and for the supremacy in every three kinds of resources.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game can be played from 2 to 6 players but it has a solitaire mode also.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Konsorcjum is language independent and comes with Polish, French, English, Spanish and Portuguese rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
